featured_reviews.review_id: It is the Oldest Mosque in Vandavasi since olden days. Though it's small mosque but has very enough space & mosque is situated in centre of the place, it's near by market, Bus stand & theradi, schools, banks etc. So this Mosque is situated in Hot place of vandavasi. Every Vandavasi Muslim likes to pray here. When Ramzan fasting came we couldn't get a place to pray, that much crowd will be there. People from other religion also come for getting Nonbu Ganji & if any baby has illness then Hazrath pray for child & blow on child, soon child may recovered with the grace of ALLAH.

featured_reviews.review_id: One of the notable Islamic religious spot in Tiruvannamalai district ( vandavasi town). Though It situated in far from main road. The atmos is very cool and comfy to enjoy and with toilet and bathroom facilities and small shops to fulfill our basic needs. And with a huge parking area also other auto services is there. Though there is no proper drinking water. The bore well water satisfy us for our needs. Best place to visit.. May have faiths that this dharga cures some paranormal ghostly attitude of anyone and also most muslims believed that this dharga evoke positive vibes within them....Any have nice place to spend a day with family...
